snippet.title: Retro Game Store Simulator Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Would you be crazy enough to start a video game store in the middle of the 1980s crash? 

...I thought you might. In "Retro Game Store Simulator", you get to build and manage your own video game store. Coming to PC 2025.

Wishlist on Steam today!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3090010/Retro_Video_Game_Store_Simulator/
